{"tid":2211033,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"外媒P圖讚孫興慜卻激怒南韓球迷：侮辱南韓國旗","createTime":"2020-09-21T00:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T01:19:10.000Z","uid":25345,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3a181420f791f0852cd79f81d0f34fff203961c8","tid":2211033,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T00:57:57.000Z","msg":"孫興慜在英超中上演大四喜，這讓整個球壇為之驚歎，外媒集體給南韓天王送上讚譽。不過，有一家外媒卻因為稱讚孫興慜，而惹怒了南韓球迷。<br />\n<br />\n  《goal》在孫興慜上演大四喜後，P了一幅圖，熱刺隊徽中的雄雞，站在了南韓國旗上面。這家外媒的配文是：「孫興慜讓人難以置信！」<br />\n<br />\n  很顯然，《goal》的目的是稱讚孫興慜。但不曾想，這樣的P圖卻讓南韓球迷怒了。<br />\n<br />\n  一位名叫「Fans HanGuk」的粉絲表示：「這是對南韓國旗的侮辱！」另一位名叫「Fans HanGuk」的球迷表示：「這是非常無禮的行為，你在侮辱我們國家！」這位球迷還@了熱刺官推和南韓政府Twitter。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/09/20/5/5ece11815667c73c1731b8cc361329de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F09%2F20%2F5%2F5ece11815667c73c1731b8cc361329de.jpg&h=ccedc9ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51941a794725a028f535459e4b7ddc51ceb997f0","tid":2211033,"uid":65858,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T00:59:53.000Z","msg":"點解會覺得畫隻野踩住人地枝國旗係個good design<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17937ba182128fa0f2e5ba2b9dbff0f1576605d3","tid":2211033,"uid":128102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:01:47.000Z","msg":"可唔可以幫幫手讚下香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc9bdd917533aa2572bc03493f363ce67799575","tid":2211033,"uid":141681,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:02:02.000Z","msg":"隻雞平衡力幾好"},{"pid":"e51045dbd7a870a73fa46b872db518e35516b72e","tid":2211033,"uid":209890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:04:14.000Z","msg":"睇睇下都幾似百事可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e083bd128e49da0d8520bc87346a3b026bc0980a","tid":2211033,"uid":139704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor